Total Wrist Arthroplasty for Posttraumatic Wrist Osteoarthritis: A Cohort Study 
Comparing Three Indications.

Holzbauer M(1)(2), Mihalic JA(1)(2), Pollak M(1)(2), Froschauer SM(1)(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Orthopedics and Traumatology, Kepler University Hospital, 
